							src="http://changelog.ca/quote/2012/07/30/kanban_at_hootsuite/4.png"
							style="width:85%;"
						/></a>
					</p>

					<h2>5. Move items through the process</h2>
					<p>
						<a
							href="http://changelog.ca/quote/2012/07/30/kanban_at_hootsuite/5.png"
						><img
							src="http://changelog.ca/quote/2012/07/30/kanban_at_hootsuite/5.png"
							style="width:85%;"
						/></a>
					</p>
					<p>
						[Process is to move cards from left to right one column at a time, excluding the "Impeded" column.
						Usual flow is:
						<em>Triage</em> &#8594; <em>Queued</em> &#8594; <em>In Development</em> &#8594; <em>In Review</em> &#8594; <em>Ready for QA</em> &#8594; <em>QA</em> &#8594; <em>Ready to Release</em>.]
					</p>

					<h2>6. Measure Time to Complete a Cycle</h2>
					<p>
						<a
							href="http://changelog.ca/quote/2012/07/30/kanban_at_hootsuite/6.png"
