							src="http://changelog.ca/quote/2012/07/30/kanban_at_hootsuite/6.png"
							style="width:85%;"
						/></a>
					</p>
					<p>
						[Cycle time starts at <em>Queued</em> and ends at <em>Ready to Release</em>.]
					</p>

